562
00:37:24,283 --> 00:37:27,495
nessa situação já tão dolorosa?

563
00:37:31,374 --> 00:37:32,500
Srta. Hayes?

564
00:37:41,968 --> 00:37:42,969
E o Caputo?

565
00:37:43,052 --> 00:37:46,973
